.text:000033CC dhcp_recv			       ; DATA XREF: dhcp_inc_pcb_refcount+66o

.text:00005598		       EXPORT ip4addr_ntoa

.text:00005598
.text:00005598 addr	       = -4

.text:000055A4		       LDR     R0, [R7,#8+addr]	; addr
.text:000055A6		       BL      ip4addr_ntoa_r
.text:000055AA		       MOV     R3, R0
.text:000055AC		       MOV     R0, R3
.text:000055AE		       ADDS    R7, #8
.text:000055B0		       MOV     SP, R7
.text:000055B2		       POP     {R7,PC}
.text:000055B2 ; End of	function ip4addr_ntoa

.text:00013240 ; =============== S U B R O U T I N E =======================================
.text:00013240
.text:00013240 ; Attributes: bp-based frame fpd=0x18
.text:00013240
.text:00013240 ; status_t __cdecl FLASH_Erase(flash_config_t *config, uint32_t start, uint32_t lengthInBytes, uint32_t key)
.text:00013240		       EXPORT FLASH_Erase
.text:00013240 FLASH_Erase
.text:00013240
.text:00013240 key	       = -0x18
.text:00013240 lengthInBytes   = -0x14
.text:00013240 start	       = -0x10
.text:00013240 config	       = -0xC
.text:00013240 flashIndex      = -5
.text:00013240 returnCode      = -4
.text:00013240
.text:00013240		       PUSH    {R7,LR}
.text:00013242		       SUB     SP, SP, #0x18
.text:00013244		       ADD     R7, SP, #0
.text:00013246		       STR     R0, [R7,#0x18+config]
.text:00013248		       STR     R1, [R7,#0x18+start]
.text:0001324A		       STR     R2, [R7,#0x18+lengthInBytes]
.text:0001324C		       STR     R3, [R7,#0x18+key]
.text:0001324E		       ADD.W   R3, R7, #0x13   ; flashIndex
.text:00013252		       LDR     R2, [R7,#0x18+lengthInBytes] ; lengthInBytes
.text:00013254		       LDR     R1, [R7,#0x18+start] ; start
.text:00013256		       LDR     R0, [R7,#0x18+config] ; config
.text:00013258		       BL      flash_check_range_to_get_index
.text:0001325C		       STR     R0, [R7,#0x18+returnCode]
.text:0001325E		       LDR     R3, [R7,#0x18+returnCode]
.text:00013260		       CMP     R3, #0
.text:00013262		       BEQ     loc_13268
.text:00013264		       LDR     R3, [R7,#0x18+returnCode]
.text:00013266		       B       loc_132A4
.text:00013268 ; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.text:00013268
.text:00013268 loc_13268			       ; CODE XREF: FLASH_Erase+22j
.text:00013268		       LDRB    R3, [R7,#0x18+flashIndex]
.text:0001326A		       MOV     R2, R3
.text:0001326C		       MOVS    R3, #0x64 ; 'd'
.text:0001326E		       MUL.W   R3, R3, R2
.text:00013272		       LDR     R2, [R7,#0x18+config]
